---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="ICON Injection Molding — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="ICON Injection Molding deployed a $10/hour Formic Tend system to automate handling of 300-degree parts at its Phoenix plant — boosting production 20% and cutting OpEx 40% from day one, with zero capital."
  ogTitle="ICON Injection Molding — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="20% more production · 40% lower OpEx · 30% faster cycle time"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/icon-injection-molding" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>ICON Injection Molding
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · ICON Injection Molding</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">ICON Injection Molding Deploys Formic Tend to Boost Production by 20% with Automation Partnership that is "Too Good to be True"</h1>
    <p class="lede">At its Phoenix plant, ICON had operators handling 300-degree parts for 8–10 hours a day. A $10/hour Formic Tend system automated the load/unload — boosting production 20% and cutting OpEx 40% from day one, with zero capital up front.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/icon-injection-molding-hero.jpg" alt="ICON Injection Molding Formic Tend automation cell" />
      <span class="dv-cap">ICON Injection Molding · Phoenix, AZ</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">2001</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Phoenix, Arizona</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Plastic injection molding</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Products</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Medical & defense parts</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Contract</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">3-year term · $10/hour</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>300-degree parts, <em>8 to 10 hours a day</em>.</h2>
      <p>At ICON's Phoenix, Arizona facility, manual operators handled 300-degree hot plastic parts 8–10 hours a day — driving turnover, injuries, and inconsistent output even when machine cycle times stayed steady. The barriers to automating were familiar: capital budget limits, maintenance cost, the inability to handle dynamic lower-volume jobs, and worker-replacement concerns.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>300-degree parts handled 8–10 hours a day</li>
        <li>Turnover, injuries, and inconsistent output</li>
        <li>Capital and flexibility barriers to automating</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/icon-injection-molding-2.jpg" alt="Formic Tend cell automating injection-molding load and unload" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Load / unload · automated</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg" alt="Six-axis FANUC robot arm tending a molding machine" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">FANUC arm · $10/hour</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>All reward, <em>no risk</em>.</h2>
      <p>Formic offered an OpEx-based approach with zero upfront capital. ICON signed a three-year contract for a customized Formic Tend system at a $10/hour usage fee, pairing a six-axis FANUC robot arm with a vertical conveyor to automate load/unload and the cooling-bath process. The flat hourly rate bundles a dedicated success team, 24/7 remote monitoring, lifetime maintenance, and equipment repurposing.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>3-year contract at a $10/hour usage fee</li>
        <li>6-axis FANUC arm + vertical conveyor</li>
        <li>Monitoring, lifetime maintenance, and repurposing included</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"When we were considering Formic, it was all reward, no risks. I couldn't come up with a good reason to say no."</blockquote>
      <cite>Jeff Galindo · Executive Operations Specialist, ICON Injection Molding</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Results</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">20% more production. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">From day one.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">20%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Production boost</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">40%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Lower OpEx, day one</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">30%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Faster cycle time</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Make it <em>too good to pass up</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
